false" ParaShape="13" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="29"><SECDEF CharGrid="0" FirstBorder="false" FirstFill="false" LineGrid="0" OutlineShape="1" SpaceColumns="1134" TabStop="8000" TextDirection="0" TextVerticalWidthHead="0"><STARTNUMBER Equation="0" Figure="0" Page="0" PageStartsOn="Both" Table="0"/><HIDE Border="false" EmptyLine="false" Fill="false" Footer="false" Header="false" MasterPage="false" PageNumPos="false"/><PAGEDEF GutterType="LeftOnly" Height="84188" Landscape="0" Width="59528"><PAGEMARGIN Bottom="4251" Footer="4251" Gutter="0" Header="4251" Left="8503" Right="8503" Top="5669"/></PAGEDEF><FOOTNOTESHAPE><AUTONUMFORMAT SuffixChar=")" Superscript="false" Type="Digit"/><NOTELINE Length="5cm" Type="Solid" Width="0.12mm"/><NOTESPACING AboveLine="850" BelowLine="567" BetweenNotes="283"/><NOTENUMBERING NewNumber="1" Type="Continuous"/><NOTEPLACEMENT BeneathText="false" Place="EachColumn"/></FOOTNOTESHAPE><ENDNOTESHAPE><AUTONUMFORMAT SuffixChar=")" Superscript="false" Type="Digit"/><NOTELINE Length="14692344" Type="Solid" Width="0.12mm"/><NOTESPACING AboveLine="850" BelowLine="567" BetweenNotes="0"/><NOTENUMBERING NewNumber="1" Type="Continuous"/><NOTEPLACEMENT BeneathText="false" Place="EndOfDocument"/></ENDNOTESHAPE><PAGEBORDERFILL FillArea="Paper" FooterInside="false" HeaderInside="false" TextBorder="true" Type="Both"><PAGEOFFSET Bottom="1417" Left="1417" Right="1417" Top="1417"/></PAGEBORDERFILL><PAGEBORDERFILL FillArea="Paper" FooterInside="false" HeaderInside="false" TextBorder="true" Type="Even"><PAGEOFFSET Bottom="1417" Left="1417" Right="1417" Top="1417"/></PAGEBORDERFILL><PAGEBORDERFILL FillArea="Paper" FooterInside="false" HeaderInside="false" TextBorder="true" Type="Odd"><PAGEOFFSET Bottom="1417" Left="1417" Right="1417" Top="1417"/></PAGEBORDERFILL></SECDEF><COLDEF Count="1" Layout="Left" SameGap="0" SameSize="true" Type="Newspaper"/><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="13" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="29"><CHAR>동적 최대화이론</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="27"/></P><P ColumnBreak="false" PageBreak="true" ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="27"><CHAR>개요</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="27"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>미사일의 최적 시간경로를 구한다든지, 한 점에서 다른 점까지 가장 빠른 시간에 도달하는 경로를 구한다든지, 전체기간의 기업의 이윤을 극대화하는 산출량을 구한다든지..., 각 시기별 최적의 시간경로를 구하는 문제는 다양한 분야에서 발생한다.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>시간을 0과 자연수로 구분하여 각 기간 최적경로를 파악하는 문제를 이산형 모형이라 한다. 반대로 시간을 실수의 연속 집합으로 보아 최적 경로를 파악하는 문제를 연속형 모형이라 한다.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="1"><CHAR>정태적 최대화 문제</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><EQUATION BaseLine="72" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1399122669" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="809"><SIZE Height="1177" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="6530" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>f(x  _{1} ,x  _{2} ,...,x  _{n} )</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>를 n 개의 상품(</CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="72" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1401626241" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="993"><SIZE Height="1190" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="5830" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>x  _{i} `,`i=1,...,n</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>)을 생산하는 기업의 이윤함수라 하면 이 기업의 이윤극대화 문제는 다음과 같다.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><EQUATION BaseLine="24" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1399122671" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="806"><SIZE Height="3580" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="11490" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>it max````f(x  _{1} ,x  _{2} ,...,x  _{n} )#
#
s.t`````````````x  _{i}  GEQ 0`,```````i=1,...,n</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="1"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="1"><CHAR>다기간(multiperiod) 이산시간(discrete time) 문제</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>이윤함수를 극대화하도록 t기에 생산되는 하나의 상품 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="72" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1399122672" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="808"><SIZE Height="1177" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="900" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>x  _{t}</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR> , t=1,...,T 를 선택</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><EQUATION BaseLine="63" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1399122673" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="807"><SIZE Height="2700" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="6250" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>it max`` sum _{t=1} ^{T} f(x  _{t} )</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><EQUATION BaseLine="72" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1399122674" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="811"><SIZE Height="1190" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="10465" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>s.t```````x  _{t}  GEQ 0`,```t=1,...,T</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>t기에 생산되는 제품량이 그 기간의 이윤함수에만 영향을 미친다고 가정하면 이 문제는 단지 정태적 문제를 T번 연속해서 푸는 것과 같다. 각각 단일변수로 구성된 T개의 1차 조건을 각각 만족시키는 해를 구하면 됨.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>t기에 생산되는 제품량이 t기는 물론 다음 기간의 이윤함수에도 영향을 미친다고 가정하면 문제는 복잡해 진다.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><EQUATION BaseLine="63" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1399122675" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="810"><SIZE Height="2700" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="9581" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>it max`` sum _{i=1} ^{T} f(x  _{t} ,`x  _{t-1} ,`t)</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><EQUATION BaseLine="72" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1399122676" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="812"><SIZE Height="1190" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="21100" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>s.t```````x  _{i}  GEQ 0``for```i=1,...,T```and``x  _{i} =x  _{0} `for`i=0</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>이 경우 T개의 1차 조건은 독립적으로 풀 수 없고 순차적으로 풀어야 한다.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="1"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="1"><CHAR>■ 다기간(multiperiod) 연속시간(continuous time) 문제</CHAR></TEXT><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>현재의 이윤은 현재의 제품생산량 뿐만 아니라 생산량 변화율에 따라 영향을 받는다면 문제는 다음과 같이 설정된다.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><EQUATION BaseLine="62" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1399122677" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="813"><SIZE Height="2586" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="12945" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>it max````````  int _{0} ^{T} {f(x(t),`x prime (t)} ,``t)dx</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><EQUATION BaseLine="72" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1399122678" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="814"><SIZE Height="1190" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="12165" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>s.t``````````````x(t) GEQ 0,``````x(0)=x  _{0}</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>, for </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="86" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1401626240" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="992"><SIZE Height="1000" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="5090" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>0` LEQ `t` LEQ `T</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>시간t를 무한히 잘게 쪼게 연속변수로 보고 시간 변화에 따른 최적값을 구하는 것이다. 이 경우 해의 도출은 미분방정식으로 표현된다.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ColumnBreak="false" PageBreak="true" ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="27"><CHAR>이산형 모형(discrete time model)</CHAR></TEXT><TEXT CharShape="14"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="14"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>이산형의 동적 최적화 문제를 푸는 데는 세 가지 방법이 있다. 하나는 KKT 조건을 다기간 모형에 확장하여 적용하는 방법이다. 또 하나는 최적제어이론(optimal control theory)이다. 다른 하나는 동적계획법(dynamic programming)이다.</CHAR></TEXT><TEXT CharShape="14"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="14"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="14"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="14"><CHAR>동적 라그랑지 방법(Dynamic Lagrangian method)</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="27"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="1"><CHAR>기간이 유한인 경우</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>단순히 KKT 조건을 다기간 제약식에 적용하는 것이다.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>다음의 다기간 최대화 문제를 고려하자.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>max </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="63" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1392243314" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="608"><SIZE Height="2700" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="5295" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>sum _{t=0} ^{T} f(u  _{t} ,`y  _{t} )</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>s.t </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="72" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1392243315" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="609"><SIZE Height="1190" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="9336" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>y  _{t+1} `=`y  _{t} `+`g(u  _{t} ,`y  _{t} )</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>, for </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="86" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1392500314" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="611"><SIZE Height="1000" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="6055" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>t`=`0,`1,`...,`T</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><EQUATION BaseLine="76" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1392500315" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="612"><SIZE Height="1372" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="3025" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>y  _{0} `=` {bar{y}}</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>, </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="72" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1392500312" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="610"><SIZE Height="1190" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="4466" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>y  _{T+1} ` GEQ `0</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>.........</CHAR><FOOTNOTE><PARALIST LineWrap="Break" LinkListID="0" LinkListIDNext="0" TextDirection="0" VertAlign="Top"><P ParaShape="1" Style="11"><TEXT CharShape="11"><AUTONUM Number="1" NumberType="Footnote"><AUTONUMFORMAT SuffixChar=")" Superscript="false" Type="Digit"/></AUTONUM><CHAR> 최종 상태 후 음이 되지 말아야 한다는 의미로 경제학 모형에서 흔히 채택되는 조건</CHAR></TEXT></P></PARALIST></FOOTNOTE><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>동태문제의 경우 제약식을 특히 </CHAR></TEXT><TEXT CharShape="19"><CHAR>운동방정식(equation of motion)</CHAR></TEXT><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>이라 부른다.</CHAR><FOOTNOTE><PARALIST LineWrap="Break" LinkListID="0" LinkListIDNext="0" TextDirection="0" VertAlign="Top"><P ParaShape="1" Style="11"><TEXT CharShape="11"><AUTONUM Number="2" NumberType="Footnote"><AUTONUMFORMAT SuffixChar=")" Superscript="false" Type="Digit"/></AUTONUM><CHAR> 이 용어의 기원은 역학에서 운동상태를 묘사하는데서 기인, 이를 또는 전환방정식(transition equation)이라 부름.</CHAR></TEXT></P></PARALIST></FOOTNOTE><CHAR> 여기서 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="72" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1392500318" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="614"><SIZE Height="1177" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="900" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>u  _{t}</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>는 의사결정자가 결정하므로 </CHAR></TEXT><TEXT CharShape="19"><CHAR>통제변수(control variable)</CHAR></TEXT><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>라 부른다. </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="72" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1392500319" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="615"><SIZE Height="1177" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="825" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>y  _{t}</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>는 통제변수의 결정에 따라 운동방정식에서 결정되므로 </CHAR></TEXT><TEXT CharShape="19"><CHAR>상태변수(state variable)</CHAR></TEXT><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>라 부른다.</CHAR><FOOTNOTE><PARALIST LineWrap="Break" LinkListID="0" LinkListIDNext="0" TextDirection="0" VertAlign="Top"><P ParaShape="1" Style="11"><TEXT CharShape="11"><AUTONUM Number="3" NumberType="Footnote"><AUTONUMFORMAT SuffixChar=")" Superscript="false" Type="Digit"/></AUTONUM><CHAR> 지금은 통제변수, 상태변수의 의미가 불분명하다 할지라도 이들 변수들의 보다 명확한 의미는 이하의 여러 예를 통해서 구체적으로 이해될 수 있다.</CHAR></TEXT></P></PARALIST></FOOTNOTE><CHAR> </CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>동태적 문제는 제약식이 상태변수의 차분방정식으로 표현되기 때문에 최적화 문제는 통제변수와 상태변수의 최적 시간경로를 구하는 것이 된다.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>각 기의 변수를 다른 변수로 보면 문제는 (T+2)개의 등식 제약식과 1개의 비음조건 제약식으로 구성되어 있으므로 KKT 조건을 이용해서 풀 수 있다.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>이 문제의 라그란지안을 만들면</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><EQUATION BaseLine="63" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1392500317" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="613"><SIZE Height="2700" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="30177" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>L`=` sum _{t=0} ^{T} [f(u  _{t} ,`y  _{t} )`+` lambda   _{t} [g(u  _{t} ,`y  _{t} )`+`y  _{t} `-`y  _{t+1} ]]`+ mu ( {bar{y}} `-`y  _{0} )`+` eta y  _{T+1} `</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><EQUATION BaseLine="72" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1393340331" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="616"><SIZE Height="1177" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="900" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>lambda   _{t}</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>,(</CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="86" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1396874226" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="671"><SIZE Height="1000" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="4785" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>t=0,`...,`T</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>), </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="86" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1398379292" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="675"><SIZE Height="975" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="600" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>mu</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>, </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="86" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1393340332" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="617"><SIZE Height="975" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="525" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>eta </SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>는 </CHAR></TEXT><TEXT CharShape="19"><CHAR>라그랑지 승수</CHAR></TEXT><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>로 동태적 문제의 경우 </CHAR></TEXT><TEXT CharShape="19"><CHAR>costate 변수, </CHAR></TEXT><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>또는 </CHAR></TEXT><TEXT CharShape="19"><CHAR>adjoint 변수</CHAR></TEXT><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>라고도 부른다.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>이 문제의 KKT 조건은 다음과 같다.</CHAR><FOOTNOTE><PARALIST LineWrap="Break" LinkListID="0" LinkListIDNext="0" TextDirection="0" VertAlign="Top"><P ParaShape="1" Style="11"><TEXT CharShape="11"><AUTONUM Number="4" NumberType="Footnote"><AUTONUMFORMAT SuffixChar=")" Superscript="false" Type="Digit"/></AUTONUM><CHAR> 등식일 경우 라그란지안 함수 최대화조건, 부등식일 경우 complementary slackness 조건으로 표현한다. 극대화 문제 ‘KKT 조건’ 참조.</CHAR></TEXT></P></PARALIST></FOOTNOTE><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><EQUATION BaseLine="61" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1393340334" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="618"><SIZE Height="2452" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="11545" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>{Partial L} over {Partial u  _{t}} `=` {Partial f} over {Partial u  _{t}} `+` lambda   _{t} {Partial g} over {Partial u  _{t}} `=`0</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>, for </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="86" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1393340336" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="619"><SIZE Height="1000" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="6055" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>t`=`0,`1,`...,`T</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR/></TEX