1"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="1" Style="11"><TEXT CharShape="8"><EQUATION BaseLine="62" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1397512082" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="673"><SIZE Height="2553" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="8000" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>lambda   _{t} `=`- {Partial f} over {Partial u  _{t}} ` bigg /  {Partial g} over {Partial u  _{t}}</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="1" Style="11"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="1" Style="11"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>따라서 transversality 조건은</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="1" Style="11"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="1" Style="11"><TEXT CharShape="8"><EQUATION BaseLine="62" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1397512084" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="674"><SIZE Height="2553" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="12031" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>lim _{t -&gt;  INF } {LEFT (- {Partial f} over {Partial u  _{t}} ` bigg / } {Partial g} over {Partial u  _{t}}  RIGHT )  y  _{t+1} `=`0</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="19" Style="11"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="19" Style="11"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>예) 다음의 재산 제약하의 효용극대화 문제를 고려하자. 생존기간은 무한대이다.</CHAR><FOOTNOTE><PARALIST LineWrap="Break" LinkListID="0" LinkListIDNext="0" TextDirection="0" VertAlign="Top"><P ParaShape="1" Style="11"><TEXT CharShape="11"><AUTONUM Number="22" NumberType="Footnote"><AUTONUMFORMAT SuffixChar=")" Superscript="false" Type="Digit"/></AUTONUM><CHAR> 개인의 생존기간이 무한대라는 가정은 비현실적이나 자손의 효용도 고려하는 이타적인 사람을 가정. 이 경우 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="84" BaseUnit="800" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1400066956" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="886"><SIZE Height="825" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="450" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>beta </SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>는 자손의 만족이 본인의 효용에 부여하는 가중치를 의미한다. </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="84" BaseUnit="800" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1400066957" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="887"><SIZE Height="825" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="1961" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>beta `&lt;`1</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>은 자손보다 자신의 만족에 더 비중을 둔다는 의미이다.</CHAR></TEXT></P></PARALIST></FOOTNOTE><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>maximize </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="63" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor