rzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>`(1+r) beta </SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR> ≶ 1 에 따른 소비패턴은 기간이 유한인 경우와 같다. 단 소비는 무한한 기간 동안 이루어지는 것이 최적이다. 특정 유한한 기간 동안에 모든 소비를 끝내고 남은 기간 소비를 안 하는 것은 최적이 아니다.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>재산의 경로는</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><EQUATION BaseLine="76" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1399122870" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="869"><SIZE Height="1365" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="17957" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>a  _{t+1} `=`(1+r)a  _{t} `-`(1+r)  ^{t+1}  beta   ^{t} (1- beta )A</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="14" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>(풀이끝)</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="19" Style="11"><TEXT CharShape="1"><CHAR>no Ponzi game 조건</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="2" Style="11"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="2" Style="11"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>재산 {</CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="72" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1400067217" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="903"><SIZE Height="1177" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="825" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>a  _{t}</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>}의 비음조건이 없다면 오일러등식과 제약식을 만족하면서도 무제한의 차입을 통해 소비를 최대화할 수 있다. 이를 방지하기 위해 재산 {</CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="72" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1400067219" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="904"><SIZE Height="1177" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="825" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>a  _{t}</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>}의 비음조건 대신 더 폭 넓은 조건인 다음의 조건을 추가할 수 있다. </CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="2" Style="11"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="2" Style="11"><TEXT CharShape="8"><EQUATION BaseLine="64" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1400067207" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="901"><SIZE Height="2640" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="8916" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>lim _{t -&gt;  INF } {{a  _{t+1}} over {(1+r)  ^{t+1}}} ` GEQ `0</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR> </CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="2" Style="11"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="2" Style="11"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>이는 먼 미래에 재산의 현재가치가 0 보다 크면 된다는 조건이므로 중간에 어느 정도의 부채를 인정한다. 이 조건을 </CHAR></TEXT><TEXT CharShape="19"><CHAR>no Ponzi game 조건</CHAR></TEXT><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>이라 한다.</CHAR><FOOTNOTE><PARALIST LineWrap="Break" LinkListID="0" LinkListIDNext="0" TextDirection="0" VertAlign="Top"><P ParaShape="1" Style="11"><TEXT CharShape="11"><AUTONUM Number="26" NumberType="Footnote"><AUTONUMFORMAT SuffixChar=")" Superscript="false" Type="Digit"/></AUTONUM><CHAR> Ponzi 게임이란 미국의 사기꾼 Ponzi가 개발한 사업으로 다단계같이 또 다른 회원을 가입시켜 그 투자금으로 기존의 돈을 투자한 회원의 이자를 지급하는 사업을 말한다. 이와 같이 무한정한 차입은 결국 파산을 불러오기 때문에 no Ponzi game 조건이란 무제한의 차입을 제한하는 것을 의미한다. </CHAR></TEXT></P></PARALIST></FOOTNOTE><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="2" Style="11"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>no Ponzi game(nPg) 조건은 최적해에서 등식으로 만족해야 한다. 최적해에서 재산이 남는 것은 추가적으로 소비할 재산이 있다는 의미이므로 더 효용을 증가시킬 수 있으므로 최적해의 가정에 위배된다. 따라서 최적해에서 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="64" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1400067209" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="902"><SIZE Height="2640" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="8691" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>lim _{t -&gt;  INF } {{a  _{t+1}} over {(1+r)  ^{t+1}}} `=`0</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>.</CHAR><FOOTNOTE><PARALIST LineWrap="Break" LinkListID="0" LinkListIDNext="0" TextDirection="0" VertAlign="Top"><P ParaShape="1" Style="11"><TEXT CharShape="11"><AUTONUM Number="27" NumberType="Footnote"><AUTONUMFORMAT SuffixChar=")" Superscript="false" Type="Digit"/></AUTONUM><CHAR> 이런 이유로 부등식이 아닌 등식을 nPg 조건으로 보기도 한다.</CHAR></TEXT></P></PARALIST></FOOTNOTE><CHAR> 이는 앞에서 보았듯이 TVC를 의미한다. 따라서 최적해에서 nPg조건은 TVC과 같기 때문에 경제모형에서 단순히 재산의 비음조건을 추가하기보다 더 완화된 조건인 nPg 조건을 추가함으로써 비음조건과 TVC를 만족하는 것으로 가정한다. </CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="2" Style="11"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="2" Style="11"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>예) 다음 문제의 오일러 방정식을 구하라</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>max </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="63" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1418305885" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="1798"><SIZE Height="2700" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="4725" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>sum _{t=0} ^{INF }  beta   ^{t} u(c  _{t} )</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>s.t  </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="72" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1418305886" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="1799"><SIZE Height="1190" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="7941" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>k  _{t+1} `=`f(k  _{t} )`-`c  _{t}</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>, </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="86" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1418305887" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="1800"><SIZE Height="1000" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="5980" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>t=0,`1,...,` INF </SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>(풀이)</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>이 문제의 라그랑지 함수를 만들면</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><EQUATION BaseLine="63" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1418305906" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="1801"><SIZE Height="2700" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="18576" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>L`=` sum _{t=0} ^{INF }  beta   ^{t} [u(c  _{t} )`+` lambda   _{t} [f(k  _{t} )`-`c  _{t} `-k  _{t+1} ]]``</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><EQUATION BaseLine="72" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1418305907" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="1806"><SIZE Height="1177" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="900" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>lambda   _{t}</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>,(</CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="86" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1418305908" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="1807"><SIZE Height="1000" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="4785" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>t=0,`...,`T</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>)는 라그랑지 승수</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>KKT 조건은 </CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><EQUATION BaseLine="61" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1418305910" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="1802"><SIZE Height="2452" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="10115" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>{Partial L} over {Partial c  _{t}} `=`u'(c  _{t} )`-` lambda   _{t} `=`0</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>, for </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="86" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1418305911" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="1803"><SIZE Height="1000" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="6355" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>t`=`0,`1,`...,` INF </SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR> ............①</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><EQUATION BaseLine="61" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1418305912" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="1808"><SIZE Height="2452" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="18754" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>{Partial L} over {Partial k  _{t+1}} `=`- beta   ^{t}  lambda   _{t} `+` beta   ^{t+1}  lambda   _{t+1} f'(k  _{t+1} )`=`0</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>, for </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="86" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1418305913" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="1809"><SIZE Height="1000" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="6355" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>t`=`0,`1,`...,` INF </SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR> ..............②</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><EQUATION BaseLine="61" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1418305914" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="1804"><SIZE Height="2452" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="13116" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>{Partial L} over {Partial  lambda   _{t}} `=f(k  _{t} )`-`c  _{t} `-`k  _{t+1} `=`0</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR> .............③</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><EQUATION BaseLine="53" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1418305916" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="1805"><SIZE Height="1950" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="7616" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>lim _{t -&gt;  INF } {beta   ^{t}  lambda   _{t}} k  _{t+1} `=`0</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>............④</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>①, ②에서</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><EQUATION BaseLine="72" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1418305923" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="1810"><SIZE Height="1190" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="12347" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>`u prime (c  _{t} )`=`f'(k  _{t+1} ) beta u prime (c  _{t+1} )</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>이는 오일러등식이다.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="14" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>(풀이끝)</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ColumnBreak="false" PageBreak="true" ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="14"><CHAR>최적화 원리(Maximum principle)</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="14"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>최적제어이론의 이산형이라 할 수 있다. 다음의 문제를 고려하자.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>max </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="63" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1399122798" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="837"><SIZE Height="2700" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="5436" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>sum _{t=0} ^{T-1} f(u  _{t} ,`y  _{t} )</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaS