 Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>H  _{t} (u  _{t} ,`y  _{t} ,` lambda   _{t+1} )`=f`(u  _{t} ,`y  _{t} )`+` lambda   _{t+1} g(u  _{t} ,`y  _{t} )</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>이 함수를 </CHAR></TEXT><TEXT CharShape="19"><CHAR>Hamiltonian</CHAR></TEXT><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>이라 부른다.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>Hamiltonian을 라그란지안에 대입하면</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><EQUATION BaseLine="63" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1399122805" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="841"><SIZE Height="2700" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="20047" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>`L`=` sum _{t=1} ^{T} [H  _{t} `- lambda   _{t+1} (y  _{t+1} -y  _{t} )]+` lambda   _{0} (A`-`y  _{0} )</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR> </CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>필요조건은</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><EQUATION BaseLine="64" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1399122806" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="842"><SIZE Height="2654" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="7590" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap