Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>여기서 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="72" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1401022560" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="978"><SIZE Height="1190" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="1250" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>lambda   _{T} `</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>는 말기 상태변수의 해당 제약식에 대응하는 라그랑지 승수이다.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><EQUATION BaseLine="72" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1401022562" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="979"><SIZE Height="1190" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="3295" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>y  _{T} `=`B</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR> 일 경우 최대화 문제일 때 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="72" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1401022564" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="980"><SIZE Height="1190" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="3370" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRel