true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>=`max  _{u  _{t}} ` LEFT { f  _{t} (y  _{t} ,``u  _{t} )+ beta [pV[g  _{t} (y  _{t} ,`u  _{t} ,` {bar{epsilon }} )]`+`(1-p)V[g  _{t} (y  _{t} ,`u  _{t} ,` {under{epsilon )}} ]] RIGHT }</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>, (∵ t기의 값은 결정된 값)</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><EQUATION BaseLine="72" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1420609421" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="1930"><SIZE Height="1177" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="1050" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>E  _{t}</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>는 t기의 기댓값을 의미한다. 가치함수가 기댓값이므로 엄밀히 표현하면 Bellman 방정식은 다음과 같을 것이다.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><EQUATION BaseLine="63" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1420609422" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="1931"><SIZE Height="1367" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="27449" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>V(y  _{t} )=`max  _{u  _{t}} ` LEFT { f  _{t} (y  _{t} ,``u  _{t} )+ beta E  _{t} E  _{t+1} E  _{t+2}  CDOTS [V(y  _{t+1} ,` epsilon   _{t+1} )] RIGHT }</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>그러나 연쇄 기대값의 법칙(law of iterated expectations)에 따라</CHAR><FOOTNOTE><PARALIST LineWrap="Break" LinkListID="0" LinkListIDNext="0" TextDirection="0" VertAlign="Top"><P ParaShape="1" Style="11"><TEXT CharShape="11"><AUTONUM Number="75" NumberType="Footnote"><AUTONUMFORMAT SuffixChar=")" Superscript="false" Type="Digit"/></AUTONUM><CHAR> 확률 ‘연쇄기대값의 법칙’ 참조</CHAR></TEXT></P></PARALIST></FOOTNOTE><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><EQUATION BaseLine="72" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1420609423" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="1932"><SIZE Height="1190" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="12158" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>E  _{t} E  _{t+1} (X  _{t+j} )`=`E  _{t} (X  _{t+j} )</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR> for j=0,1, 2, ...</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>따라서 Bellman 방정식은 위와 같이 표현된다.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>일반적으로 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="72" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1420609396" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="1918"><SIZE Height="1177" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="750" Wi