IPT>epsilon   _{t+1}</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>는 기간간 상관관계가 있을 수도 있지만 Markov 특성을 갖는다고 가정. Markov 특성이란 현재의 확률변수가 바로 전기의 확률에만 의존하는 것을 말한다. 즉 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="72" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1420609403" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="1922"><SIZE Height="1177" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="1921" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>epsilon   _{t+1}</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>의 분포는 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="72" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1420609404" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="1923"><SIZE Height="1177" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="750" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>epsilon   _{t}</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>에 의존하지만 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="72" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1420609405" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="1924"><SIZE Height="1177" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="1921" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>epsilon   _{t-1}</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>, </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="72" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1420609406" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="1925"><SIZE Height="1177" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="1921" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>epsilon   _{t-2}</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>, ...와는 상관이 없다.</CHAR></TEXT></P></PARALIST></FOOTNOTE><CHAR> Bellman 방정식은 다음과 같다.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><EQUATION BaseLine="63" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1420609399" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="1920"><SIZE Height="1367" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="21547" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>V(y  _{t} )=`max  _{u  _{t}} ` LEFT { f  _{t} (y  _{t} ,``u  _{t} )+ beta E  _{t} [V(y  _{t+1} ,` epsilon   _{t+1} )] RIGHT }</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR> </CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="21" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>예) 예산 제약하의 효용극대화 문제에서 동적계획법으로 오일러 방정식을 도출하라.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" St