ype="Equation" ZOrder="2020"><SIZE Height="2654" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="18747" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>` {Partial V  _{t} (K  _{t} )} over {Partial K  _{t}} `=`` {Partial F} over {Partial K  _{t}} `+` {1- delta } over {1+r} {Partial V  _{t+1} (K  _{t+1} )} over {Partial K  _{t+1}} `</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>, (∵ </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="64" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1420809097" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="2021"><SIZE Height="2654" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="5391" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>` {Partial K  _{t+1}} over {Partial K  _{t}} `=` delta </SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>) ............④</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>②, ③을 ④에 대입하면</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><EQUATION BaseLine="61" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1420809098" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="2022"><SIZE Height="2452" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="9535" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>`1+r`=`` {Partial F} over {Partial K  _{t}} `+`1- delta `</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>⇒ </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="61" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1420809099" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="2024"><SIZE Height="2452" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="6025" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>`` {Partial F} over {Partial K  _{t}} `=`r+ delta `</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="1"><CHAR>이윤극대화의 조건</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>최적 노동투입량은 매기의 노동의 한계생산물이 매기의 실질임금과 같도록 결정되어야 한다.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>최적 자본투입량은 매기의 자본의 한계생산물이 매기의 이자율과 감가상각률의 합과 같도록 결정되어야 한다.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ColumnBreak="false" PageBreak="true" ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="14"><CHAR>소비 자본-자산 가격결정 모형(consumption CAPM)</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>투자자의 효용극대화를 위한 소비-저축 모형에서 저축의 방법이 여러 가지인 경우를 고려하자. 즉 투자자는 다양한 자산(증권)에 투자함으로서 재산을 증식시킬 수 있다.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>(t+1)기의 재산은 t기의 재산에서 t기의 소비를 뺀 금액에 이자율을 곱한 것이다. </CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><EQUATION BaseLine="72" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1421506436" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="2029"><SIZE Height="1190" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="10571" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>a  _{t+1} `=`(1+r  _{t} )(a  _{t} `-`c  _{t} )</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>재산에서 소비를 뺀 금액은 저축을 의미한다. </CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>이 저축을 n개의 자산(증권)에 투자하는 경우를 고려하자.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><EQUATION BaseLine="63" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1421506456" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="2030"><SIZE Height="2700" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="7229" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>sum _{i=1} ^{n} s  _{i,t} `=`a  _{t} `-`c  _{t}</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>, </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="72" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1421506458" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="2031"><SIZE Height="1177" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="1324" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>s  _{i,t}</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>는 t기에 i 자산에 투자한 저축금액</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><EQUATION BaseLine="72" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1421506459" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="2032"><SIZE Height="1177" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="1249" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>r  _{i,t}</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>를 t기에 i 자산의 투자수익률이라 하면</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><EQUATION BaseLine="63" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1421506461" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="2033"><SIZE Height="2700" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="11195" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITIO