acing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>E  _{t} (1+r  _{i,t+1} )`-(`1+r  _{t+1} ^{f} )`=`-`(1+r  _{t+1} ^{f} )Cov(1+r  _{i,t+1} ,```m  _{t+1} )</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR> ..............⑨</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>Assets whose returns have a high negative co-variance with consumption will be held with a low risk premium. Conversely, assets whose returns have a high positive covariance with consumption are not so useful when times are bad, and they will command a high risk premium to convince investors to hold them.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>This model therefore associates an asset’s systematic risk with the state of the economy(consumption).</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>자산 중에는 수익률이 기간간 한계대체율과 같은 것도 있다. 이를 k라 하면</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><EQUATION BaseLine="72" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1421506533" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="2057"><SIZE Height="1190" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="8066" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>1+r  _{k,t+1} ^{} `=`m  _{t+1}</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>이 자산 k에 대하여 ⑧은</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><EQUATION BaseLine="76" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1421506535" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="2058"><SIZE Height="1365" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="27108" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>`1+r  _{t+1} ^{f} `=E  _{t} (1+r  _{k,t+1} )`+`(1+r  _{t+1} ^{f} )Cov(1+r  _{k,t+1} ,```m  _{t+1} )</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>⇒ </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="76" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1421506537" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="2059"><SIZE Height="1365" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="20334" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>`1+r  _{t+1} ^{f} `=E  _{t} (m  _{t+1} )`+`(1+r  _{t+1} ^{f} )Var(m  _{t+1} )</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>⇒ </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="66" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1421506539" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="2060"><SIZE Height="2842" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="17848" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>`-(`1+r  _{t+1} ^{f} )`=` {E  _{t} (m  _{t+1} )-(`1+r  _{t+1} ^{f} `)} over {Var(m  _{t+1} )}</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>............⑩</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>⑩을 ⑨에 대입하면</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><EQUATION BaseLine="76" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1421506543" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="2062"><SIZE Height="1365" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="13301" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>E  _{t} (1+r  _{i,t+1} )`-(`1+r  _{t+1} ^{f} )`=`</SCRIPT></EQUATION><EQUATION BaseLine="66" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1421506545" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="2063"><SIZE Height="2842" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="10107" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>`` {Cov(m  _{t+1} ,``1+r  _{t+1} ^{f} `)} over {Var(m  _{t+1} )}</SCRIPT></EQUATION><EQUATION BaseLine="76" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1421506549" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="2064"><SIZE Height="1365" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="11017" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>``[E  _{t} (m  _{t+1} )-(`1+r  _{t+1} ^{f} `)]</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>⇒ </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="72" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1421506553" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="2065"><SIZE Height="1190" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="7545" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>E  _{t} (1+r  _{i,t+1} )`=`</SCRIPT></EQUATION><EQUATION BaseLine="86" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1421506558" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="2068"><SIZE Height="975" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="600" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>beta </SCRIPT></EQUATION><EQUATION BaseLine="76" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1421506555" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="2066"><SIZE Height="1365" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="16453" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>[E  _{t} (m  _{t+1} )-(`1+r  _{t+1} ^{f} `)]+(`1+r  _{t+1} ^{f} )`</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>where </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="66" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1421506557" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="2067"><SIZE Height="2842" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="12202" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>`` beta `=` {Cov(m  _{t+1} ,``1+r  _{t+1} ^{f} `)} over {Var(m  _{t+1} )}</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>이 공식을 소비에 기초한 자본-자산 가격결정모형(consumption CAPM)이라 부른다.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>자산 i의 기대수익률은 무위험자산의 수익률 + 한계대체율과 무위험자산 수익률의 차이에 일정 비율을 곱한 값과 같다. </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="66" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1421506561" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="2070"><SIZE Height="2842" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="10232" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>``` {Cov(m  _{t+1} ,``1+r  _{t+1} ^{f} `)} over {Var(m  _{t+1} )}</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>를 소비 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="86" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1421506559" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="2069"><SIZE Height="975" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="600" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>beta</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>라 한다.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>In the standard one-period CAPM, investors maximize their expected utility in the</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>mean-variance world. That is, their behaviour is based on the one-period mean and vari-ance of returns. In contrast, the consumption-CAPM is an intertemporal model within which investors maximize their expected lifetime utility.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ColumnBreak="false" PageBreak="true" ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="14"><CHAR>신고전학파 경제성장모형(neoclassical economic growth model)</CHAR></TEXT><TEXT CharShape="8"><FOOTNOTE><PARALIST LineWrap="Break" LinkListID="0" LinkListIDNext="0" TextDirection="0" VertAlign="Top"><P ParaShape="1" Style="11"><TEXT CharShape="11"><AUTONUM Number="97" NumberType="Footnote"><AUTONUMFORMAT SuffixChar=")" Superscript="false" Type="Digit"/></AUTONUM><CHAR> 최초 발제자의 이름을 따 </CHAR></TEXT><TEXT CharShape="42"><CHAR>Ramsey 모형</CHAR></TEXT><TEXT CharShape="11"><CHAR>, 또는 </CHAR></TEXT><TEXT CharShape="42"><CHAR>Ramsey-Cass-Koopmans 모형</CHAR></TEXT><TEXT CharShape="11"><CHAR>이라고도 한다.</CHAR></TEXT></P></PARALIST></FOOTNOTE><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="14"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>Solow 모형에서 저축은 주어진 것으로 일정한 것으로 가정했다. Ramsey 모형은 저축이 가계의 효용 극대화 원칙에 따라 결정되는 것으로 본다. </CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="1"><CHAR>가정</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>- 효용은 소비의 함수이다.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><EQUATION BaseLine="72" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1399122613" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="779"><SIZE Height="1190" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="4965" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>u  _{t} `=`u(C  _{t} )</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><EQUATION BaseLine="72" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1399122614" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="800"><SIZE Height="1177" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="1050" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>C  _{t}</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR> : t기의 소비</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="27" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>효용함수는 오목함수이고, 이나다 조건을 만족한다.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><EQUATION BaseLine="86" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1399122615" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="780"><SIZE Height="1000" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="9315" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>u prime (c)`&gt;0,````u '' (c)&lt;0</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><EQUATION BaseLine="51" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1399122616" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="781"><SIZE Height="1875" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="6510" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>lim _{c-&gt; 0} {u'(c)`=` INF }</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>, </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="51" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1399122617" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="782"><SIZE Height="1875" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="6060" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>lim _{c-&gt;  INF } {u'(c)`=`0}</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="27" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>인구는 매년 일정 비율로 증가한다. 인구는 완전고용된다.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><EQUATION BaseLine="72" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1399122618" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="797"><SIZE Height="1190" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="7736" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>L  _{t+1} `=`(1+ mu )L  _{t}</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>, </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="86" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1399122619" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="798"><SIZE Height="975" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="600" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>mu </SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>는 인구증가율(상수), </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="72" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1399122620" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="801"><SIZE Height="1177" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="975" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>L  _{t}</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR> : t기의 인구</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>⇒ </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="76" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1421506574" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="2078"><SIZE Height="1365" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="6940" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="fal