 CharShape="43"><CHAR>L</CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="68" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1421506566" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="2074"><SIZE Height="1015" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="375" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>{} _{p}</SCRIPT></EQUATION></TEXT><TEXT CharShape="11"><EQUATION BaseLine="64" BaseUnit="800" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1399122642" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="803"><SIZE Height="2159" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="22321" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>`=` sum _{t=0} ^{INF } LEFT [ beta   ^{t} L  _{0} (1+ mu )  ^{t} u(c  _{t} )`+` lambda   _{t} LEFT ( ` {f(k  _{t} )+(1- delta )k  _{t}} over {1+ mu } `- {c  _{t}} over {1+ mu } `-k  _{t+1} RIGHT ) RIGHT ]</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>. 어느 것이나 결과는 같다. 단지 라그랑지승수의 해석이 약간 달라진다.</CHAR></TEXT></P></PARALIST></FOOTNOTE><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>필요조건:</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><EQUATION BaseLine="61" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1421506562" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="2071"><SIZE Height="2452" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="1775" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>{Partial } over {Partial c  _{t}}</SCRIPT></EQUATION></TEXT><TEXT CharShape="44"><CHAR>L</CHAR></TEXT><TEXT CharShape="8"><EQUATION BaseLine="69" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1399122643" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="789"><SIZE Height="2452" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="14670" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>`=L  _{0} (1+ mu )  ^{t} u prime (c  _{t} )`-` {lambda   _{t}} over {1+ mu } `=`0`</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR> .............. ①</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><EQUATION BaseLine="61" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1421506564" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="2072"><SIZE Height="2452" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="3021" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>{Partial } over {Partial k  _{t+1}}</SCRIPT></EQUATION></TEXT><TEXT CharShape="44"><CHAR>L</CHAR></TEXT><TEXT CharShape="8"><EQUATION BaseLine="69" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1399122644" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="790"><SIZE Height="2452" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="19063" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>`=` beta   ^{t+1}  lambda   _{t+1} LEFT ( {f prime (k  _{t+1} )+1- delta } over {1+ mu } RIGHT ) `-` beta   ^{t}  lambda   _{t} `=`0</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR> ............. ②</CHAR><FOOTNOTE><PARALIST LineWrap="Break" LinkListID="0" LinkListIDNext="0" TextDirection="0" VertAlign="Top"><P ParaShape="1" Style="11"><TEXT CharShape="11"><AUTONUM Number="100" NumberType="Footnote"><AUTONUMFORMAT SuffixChar=")" Superscript="false" Type="Digit"/></AUTONUM><CHAR> </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="64" BaseUnit="800" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1399122645" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="791"><SIZE Height="2159" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="14540" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>sum _{t=0} ^{INF }  beta   ^{t}  lambda   _{t} LEFT ( ` {f(k  _{t} )+(1- delta )k  _{t}} over {1+ mu } `- {c  _{t}} over {1+ mu } `-k  _{t+1} RIGHT ) ``</SCRIPT></EQUATION><EQUATION BaseLine="68" BaseUnit="800" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1399122646" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="804"><SIZE Height="2044" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="14940" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>=` lambda   _{0} LEFT ( ` {f(k  _{0} )+(1- delta )k  _{0}} over {1+ mu } `- {c  _{0}} over {1+ mu } `-k  _{0} RIGHT ) `+` CDOTS `</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="1" Style="11"><TEXT CharShape="11"><CHAR>    </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="68" BaseUnit="800" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1399122647" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="792"><SIZE Height="2044" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="33776" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>+`` beta   ^{t}  lambda   _{t} LEFT ( ` {f(k  _{t} )+(1- delta )k  _{t}} over {1+ mu } `- {c  _{t}} over {1+ mu } `-k  _{t+1} RIGHT ) `+` beta   ^{t+1}  lambda   _{t+1} LEFT ( ` {f(k  _{t+1} )+(1- delta )k  _{t+1}} over {1+ mu } `- {c  _{t+1}} over {1+ mu } `-k  _{t+2} RIGHT ) `+` CDOTS </SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR/></TEXT></P></PARALIST></FOOTNOTE><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><EQUATION BaseLine="61" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1421506565" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="2073"><SIZE Height="2452" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="1925" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>{Partial } over {Partial  lambda   _{t}}</SCRIPT></EQUATION></TEXT><TEXT CharShape="44"><CHAR>L</CHAR></TEXT><TEXT CharShape="8"><EQUATION BaseLine="69" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1399122648" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="805"><SIZE Height="2452" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="18501" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>`=`` {f(k  _{t} )+(1- delta )k  _{t}} over {1+ mu } `- {c  _{t}} over {1+ mu } `-k  _{t+1} `=`0</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR> </CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>⇒ </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="72" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1422262497" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="2099"><SIZE Height="1190" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="16106" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>`(1+ mu )k  _{t+1} `+`c  _{t} =`` {f(k  _{t} )+(1- delta )k  _{t}}</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR> ..............③</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>①에서</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><EQUATION BaseLine="76" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1399122649" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="793"><SIZE Height="1365" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="10636" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>lambda   _{t} `=L  _{0} (1+ mu )  ^{t+1} u prime (c  _{t} )`</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>⇒ </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="76" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1399122650" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="794"><SIZE Height="1365" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="12978" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>lambda   _{t+1} `=L  _{0} (1+ mu )  ^{t+2} u prime (c  _{t+1} )`</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>이를 ②에 대입하면</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><EQUATION BaseLine="69" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1399122651" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="795"><SIZE Height="2452" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="28374" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>`L  _{0} (1+ mu )  ^{t+2}  beta u prime (c  _{t+1} )` LEFT ( {f prime (k  _{t+1} )+1- delta } over {1+ mu } RIGHT ) `=`L  _{0} (1+ mu )  ^{t+1} u prime (c  _{t} )`</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>⇒ </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="72" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1399122652" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="796"><SIZE Height="1190" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="16532" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>`u prime (c  _{t} )`=` beta u prime (c  _{t+1} )` LEFT ( {f prime (k  _{t+1} )+1- delta }  RIGHT ) `</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>...........④</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>이는 </CHAR></TEXT><TEXT CharShape="19"><CHAR>오일러 방정식,</CHAR></TEXT><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR> 또는 </CHAR></TEXT><TEXT CharShape="19"><CHAR>케인즈-램지 규칙(Keynes-Ramsey rule)</CHAR></TEXT><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>이라 한다.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>What is the intuition? The basic idea is that, if the consumption path is</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>optimal, the initial planner must be indifferent between the two alternatives:</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>1. Consume a unit of output today, reaping the utility gain </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="72" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1422262523" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="2107"><SIZE Height="1190" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="2820" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>`u prime (c  _{t} )`</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>2. Invest the output in capital instead, but consume the proceeds (including what is left of the initial amount invested) tomorrow. The proceeds are </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="72" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1422262525" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="2108"><SIZE Height="1177" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="7001" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>f prime (k  _{t+1} )+1- delta </SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>, and their marginal utility value from the stand-point of date t is the product of (a) the discount factor (1+</CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="86" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1422262526" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="2109"><SIZE Height="975" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="600" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>mu</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>) and (b) the marginal utility reaped by each member of generation t+1, </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="69" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1422262527" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="2110"><SIZE Height="2452" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="4241" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>{u'(c  _{t+1} )} over {1+ mu }</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>. Thus, the marginal gain from this second alternative is </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="72" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1422262528" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="2111"><SIZE Height="1190" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="12592" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>`` beta u prime (c  _{t+1} )` LEFT ( f prime (k  _{t+1} )+1- delta  RIGHT ) `</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>; the right-hand side of (4) above.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>③과 ④는 비선형 연립 차분방정식이다. 해를 고정시키기 위해서는 두 개의 조건이 필요하다. 하나는 초기조건으로 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="76" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1421990891" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="2095"><SIZE Height="1372" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="2865" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>k  _{0} = {bar{k}}</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>, 또 하나는 추가적으로 TVC가 필요하다. </CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>앞에서 할인율이 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="86" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1432690169" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="2397"><SIZE Height="975" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="600" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>beta </SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>일 때 TVC의 공식은</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><EQUATION BaseLine="64" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1432690167" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="2396"><SIZE Height="2667" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="15271" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>lim _{t -&gt;  INF } {LEFT ( - {Partial f(y  _{t} ,`u  _{t} )/ Partial u  _{t}} over {Partial y  _{t+1} / Partial u  _{t}} RIGHT )} y  _{t+1} ` beta   ^{t} `=`0</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR> ...................</CHAR><FOOTNOTE><PARALIST LineWrap="Break" LinkListID="0" LinkListIDNext="0" TextDirection="0" VertAlign="Top"><P ParaShape="1" Style="11"><TEXT CharShape="11"><AUTONUM Number="101" NumberType="Footnote"><AUTONUMFORMAT SuffixChar=")" Superscript="false" Type="Digit"/></AUTONUM><CHAR> 동적계획법 TVC 참조</CHAR></TEXT></P></PARALIST></FOOTNOTE><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>이를 이 문제의 유형에 맞게 대입하면 </CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><EQUATION BaseLine="64" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1432690171" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="2398"><SIZE Height="2667" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="4765" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>{ {Partial f(y  _{t} ,`u  _{t} )} over { Partial u  _{t}} }</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR> ⇒ </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="64" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1432690173" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="2399"><SIZE Height="2654" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="7360" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>{Partial u(c  _{t} )} over {Partial c  _{t}} `=`u'(c  _{t} )</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>, </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="64" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1432690174" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="2400"><SIZE Height="2654" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="3021" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>{Partial y  _{t+1}} over {Partial u  _{t}}</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR> ⇒ </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="64" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1432690176" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="2402"><SIZE Height="2654" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="6146" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>{Partial k  _{t+1}} over {Partial c  _{t}} `=`-1</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>, </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="88" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1432690177" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="2403"><SIZE Height="1175" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="6550" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>beta   ^{t} ` RARROW ` beta   ^{t} (1+ mu )  ^{t}</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>따라서 TVC는 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="53" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1421990889" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="2094"><SIZE Height="1950" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="12861" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>` lim _{t -&gt;  INF } {beta   ^{t} (1+ mu )  ^{t} u prime (c  _{t} )k  _{t+1} `=`0}</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="1"><CHAR>정상상태(steady state)</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>정상상태에서 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="72" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1422262491" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="2096"><SIZE Height="1190" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="6636" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>c  _{t} `=`c  _{t+1} `=`c*</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>, </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="72" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1422262493" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="2097"><SIZE Height="1190" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="6861" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>k  _{t} `=`k  _{t+1} `=`k*</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR> 이므로 ③, ④에서</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><EQUATION BaseLine="86" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1422262495" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="2098"><SIZE Height="1000" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="15645" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>`(1+ mu )k*`+`c*=``f(k*)+(1- delta )k*</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>⇒ </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="86" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1422262500" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="2100"><SIZE Height="1000" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="10250" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>``c*=``f(k*)-( delta + mu )k*</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>..............⑤</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><EQUATION BaseLine="86" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1422262502" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="2101"><SIZE Height="1000" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="14765" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>`u prime (c*)`=` beta u prime (c*)`[f prime (k*)+1- delta ]`</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>⇒ </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="86" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1422262504" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="2102"><SIZE Height="1000" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="9760" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>`1`=` beta `[f prime (k*)+1- delta ]`</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>...............⑥</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>⇒ </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="86" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1422262545" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="2120"><SIZE Height="1000" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="6540" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>f'(k*)`=` theta `+ delta </SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>, where </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="66" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Versio