</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>c  _{t}</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR> 는 남서쪽 또는 북동쪽에서 시작해야 한다. 또한 남서쪽 또는 북동쪽에서 시작하더라도 긍극적으로 남동쪽, 북서쪽으로 가는 경로도 제외해야 한다. 따라서 유일한 경로는 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="72" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1425961239" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="2349"><SIZE Height="1177" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="2685" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>b  _{1} =0</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>인 경로이다.</CHAR></TEXT></P></PARALIST></FOOTNOTE><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><EQUATION BaseLine="76" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1425133783" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="2315"><SIZE Height="1365" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="7805" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>k  _{t} -k*`=``b  _{2} p  _{12}  lambda   _{2} ^{t}</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR> ...............①</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><EQUATION BaseLine="76" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1425133791" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="2320"><SIZE Height="1365" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="7