 E6="0.00000"/><ROTMATRIX E1="1.00000" E2="0.00000" E3="0.00000" E4="0.00000" E5="1.00000" E6="0.00000"/><SCAMATRIX E1="1.00000" E2="0.00000" E3="0.00000" E4="0.00000" E5="1.09434" E6="0.00000"/><ROTMATRIX E1="1.00000" E2="0.00000" E3="0.00000" E4="0.00000" E5="1.00000" E6="0.00000"/></RENDERINGINFO></SHAPECOMPONENT><LINESHAPE Alpha="255" Color="16777215" EndCap="Flat" Style="Solid" Width="33"/><SHADOW Alpha="0" Color="11711154" OffsetX="0" OffsetY="0" Type="0"/><DRAWTEXT Editable="false" LastWidth="1745" Name=""><TEXTMARGIN Bottom="283" Left="283" Right="283" Top="283"/><PARALIST LineWrap="Break" LinkListID="0" LinkListIDNext="0" TextDirection="0" VertAlign="Center"><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>0</CHAR></TEXT></P></PARALIST></DRAWTEXT></DRAWINGOBJECT></RECTANGLE></CONTAINER><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><EQUATION BaseLine="72" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1443001645" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="2904"><SIZE Height="1177" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="4340" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>y(t  _{0} )=y  _{0}</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR> , </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="72" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1443001646" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="2905"><SIZE Height="1177" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="4340" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>y(t  _{1} )=y  _{1}</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>는 </CHAR></TEXT><TEXT CharShape="19"><CHAR>경계조건</CHAR></TEXT><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>이라 한다.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><EQUATION BaseLine="86" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1443001647" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="2906"><SIZE Height="1000" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="5795" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>f(y(t),`y'(t))</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>는 함수 y(t)의 함수로서 함수의 함수를 </CHAR></TEXT><TEXT CharShape="19"><CHAR>범함수(functional)</CHAR></TEXT><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>라고 한다.</CHAR><FOOTNOTE><PARALIST LineWrap="Break" LinkListID="0" LinkListIDNext="0" TextDirection="0" VertAlign="Top"><P ParaShape="1" Style="11"><TEXT CharShape="11"><AUTONUM Number="112" NumberType="Footnote"><AUTONUMFORMAT SuffixChar=")" Superscript="false" Type="Digit"/></AUTONUM><CHAR> 수학기초 ‘범함수’ 참조</CHAR></TEXT></P></PARALIST></FOOTNOTE><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="21" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>예) y(x)를  두 점 A(</CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="72" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1443001649" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="2907"><SIZE Height="1190" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="2495" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>x  _{0} ,``y  _{0}</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>), B(</CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="72" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1443001651" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="2908"><SIZE Height="1190" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="2495" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>x  _{1} ,``y  _{1}</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>)를 연결하는 길(path)이라 하면 이 경로의 길이는 범함수 f(y(t))로 표현된다. K(t)를 t기의 자본이라 한다면 국내총생산물 GDP는 범함수 f(K(t))로 표현된다. </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="66" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1443001664" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="2916"><SIZE Height="1911" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="5370" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT> int _{} ^{} {f(y(t))dt}</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR> 도 f(y(t))의 함수로 범함수이다.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="21" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="48" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>예) 독점기업의 제품 수요가 가격과 가격변화율의 함수라면 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="72" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1443001667" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="2918"><SIZE Height="1190" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="9570" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>Q  _{d} `=`Q  _{d} (P(t),`P'(t))</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>,  독점기업의 총수입은 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="72" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1443001669" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="2920"><SIZE Height="1177" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="1950" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>PQ  _{s}</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>, 총비용은 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="72" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1443001677" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="2925"><SIZE Height="1190" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="9920" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>C(Q  _{s} )`=``C[Q(P,`P prime )]</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>이다.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="48" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="48" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>수요=공급의 법칙에 따라 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="72" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1443001670" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="2921"><SIZE Height="1190" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="9400" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>Q  _{d} `=`Q  _{s} `=`Q(P,`P')</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="21" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="21" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>따라서 t 시점에서 기업의 이윤은 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="86" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1443001668" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="2919"><SIZE Height="1000" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="16825" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>pi (P,`P')`=`PQ(P,`P')`-`C[Q(P,`P')]</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="21" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>[</CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="72" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1443001672" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="2922"><SIZE Height="1190" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="2120" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>t  _{0} ,``t  _{1}</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>] 기간 동안 기업의 총이윤은 할인율을 고려하지 않는다면 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="59" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1443001673" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="2923"><SIZE Height="2719" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="6470" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT> int _{t  _{0}} ^{t  _{1}} {pi (P,`P')dt}</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>, 이는 목적식에 t가 포함 안 된 경우이다. 할인율 r을 고려한다면 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="59" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1443001675" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="2924"><SIZE Height="2719" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="8368" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT> int _{t  _{0}} ^{t  _{1}} {e  ^{-rt} pi (P,`P prime )dt}</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>, 이는 목적식에 t가 포함된 경우이다.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/