t="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT> int _{t  _{0}} ^{t  _{1}} {(f  _{yy} h  ^{2} +2f  _{yy prime } hh prime +f  _{y prime y prime } h prime   ^{2} )dt` LEQ 0``}</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR> 이면 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="72" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1440520119" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="2653"><SIZE Height="1177" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="3885" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>  f  _{y prime y prime }  LEQ 0}</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>...........</CHAR><FOOTNOTE><PARALIST LineWrap="Break" LinkListID="0" LinkListIDNext="0" TextDirection="0" VertAlign="Top"><P ParaShape="20" Style="11"><TEXT CharShape="11"><AUTONUM Number="118" NumberType="Footnote"><AUTONUMFORMAT SuffixChar=")" Superscript="false" Type="Digit"/></AUTONUM><CHAR> 자세한 증명은 M. Kamien and N. Schwarz, Dynamic Optimization : the calculus of variations and optimal control in economics and management, vol.4. pp.15-19. 1981. 참조.</CHAR></TEXT></P></PARALIST></FOOTNOTE><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>이를 2차조건 또는 </CHAR></TEXT><TEXT CharShape="19"><CHAR>르장드르 조건</CHAR></TEXT><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>이라 한다. </CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>르장드르조건은 오일러방정식에서 구한 극값(extremals)이 최대값인지 최소값인지를 구분하는 필요조건이다. </CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="21" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>※ 주의할 점은 정태적 문제와 달리 르장드르조건은 충분조건이 아니라는 점이다. 따라서 극값이면 르장드르 조건을 충족하지만 르장드르 조건을 만족한다고 해서 극값인 것은 아니다.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="21" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="21" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><TABLE BorderFill="3" CellSpacing="0" ColCount="1" PageBreak="Cell" RepeatHeader="true" RowCount="1"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1446534952" Lock="false" NumberingType="Table" ZOrder="3047"><SIZE Height="9591" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="41956" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Column" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="283" Left="283" Right="283" Top="283"/></SHAPEOBJECT><INSIDEMARGIN Bottom="141" Left="510" Right="510" Top="141"/><ROW><CELL BorderFill="3" ColAddr="0" ColSpan="1" Dirty="false" Editable="false" HasMargin="false" Header="false" Height="282" Protect="false" RowAddr="0" RowSpan="1" Width="41956"><PARALIST LineWrap="Break" LinkListID="0" LinkListIDNext="0" TextDirection="0" VertAlign="Center"><P ParaShape="21" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>(정리) </CHAR></TEXT><TEXT CharShape="19"><CHAR>Takayama 정리</CHAR></TEXT><TEXT CharShape="8"><FOOTNOTE><PARALIST LineWrap="Break" LinkListID="0" LinkListIDNext="0" TextDirection="0" VertAlign="Top"><P ParaShape="1" Style="11"><TEXT CharShape="11"><AUTONUM Number="119" NumberType="Footnote"><AUTONUMFORMAT SuffixChar=")" Superscript="false" Type="Digit"/></AUTONUM><CHAR> Takayama, mathematical economics, pp.429 참조.</CHAR></TEXT></P></PARALIST></FOOTNOTE><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="21" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><EQUATION BaseLine="86" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1446534956" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="3048"><SIZE Height="1000" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="4205" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>f(y,`y',`t)</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>가 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="86" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1446534957" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="3049"><SIZE Height="1000" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="1845" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>y,`y'</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>에 대해 미분가능이고, 또한 y(t)도 [</CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="72" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1446534958" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="3050"><SIZE Height="1190" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="1995" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>t  _{0} ,`t  _{1}</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>]에서 미분가능이다. </CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>f가 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="86" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1446534969" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="3056"><SIZE Height="1000" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="1845" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>y,`y'</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>에 대해 오목함수일 때 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="86" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1446534959" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="3051"><SIZE Height="975" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="1050" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>y*</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>가 오일러 방정식을 만족하면 </CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><EQUATION BaseLine="59" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1446534960" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="3052"><SIZE Height="2719" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="11915" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>J(y*)`=  int _{t  _{0}} ^{t  _{1}} {f(y*,`y* prime ,`t)dt}</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR> 는 극대값이다. 역도 성립</CHAR></TEXT></P></PARALIST></CELL></ROW></TABLE><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>즉 f가 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="86" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1446534971" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="3057"><SIZE Height="1000" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="1845" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>y,`y'</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>에 대해 오목함수일 때 오일러 방정식은 극대화의 필요충분조건이다. 최소화 문제의 경우는 f가 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="86" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1446534973" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="3058"><SIZE Height="1000" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="1845" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>y,`y'</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>에 대해 볼록함수여야 한다.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>(증명)</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>극대값이면 오일러 방정식을 만족함은 앞의 유도에서 보였으므로 여기서는 반대의 경우만 증명한다.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><EQUATION BaseLine="86" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1446534989" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="3068"><SIZE Height="1000" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="3035" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>y*,`y*'</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>이 오일러 방정식을 만족한다고 하고, </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="86" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1446534990" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="3069"><SIZE Height="1000" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="8015" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>f(y*,`y*',`t)`=`f*</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>라 하자.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><EQUATION BaseLine="59" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1446534991" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="3070"><SIZE Height="2719" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="29965" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>J(y