EOBJECT><SCRIPT>x=x  _{1}</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR> 직선에 이르는 무수히 많은 선분들(</CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="72" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1443001634" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="2898"><SIZE Height="1177" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="5125" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>y=c  _{1} x+c  _{2}</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>) 중 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="72" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1443001636" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="2899"><SIZE Height="1177" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="2820" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>x=x  _{1}</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>에 수직인 직선(</CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="72" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1443001638" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="2900"><SIZE Height="1177" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="2670" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>y=y  _{0}</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>)을 특화하는 역할을 한다.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>2차조건 :</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><EQUATION BaseLine="45" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1392241587" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="572"><SIZE Height="3317" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="11810" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>f  _{y prime y prime } = {1} over {(1+y prime   ^{2} )  ^{{1} over {2}} (1+y prime   ^{2} )}</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR> ≥ 0</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>따라서 르장드르조건을 만족</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="14" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>(풀이끝)</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ColumnBreak="false" PageBreak="true" ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="14"><CHAR>최적제어이론(optimal control theory)</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>최적제어이론은 통제변수가 상태변수의 도함수가 아닌 좀 더 일반적인 형태로 주어지는 경우에 문제를 푸는 것이다.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="1"><CHAR>표준형</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><EQUATION BaseLine="59" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="2036563930" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="0"><SIZE Height="2719" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="11595" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>max```  int _{t  _{0}} ^{t  _{1}} {f(y(t),`u(t),`t)dt}</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><EQUATION BaseLine="86" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="2036563931" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="1"><SIZE Height="1000" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="11455" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>s.t``````````` y prime ` `=`g(y(t),`u(t),`t)</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR> </CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>     </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="72" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="2036563932" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="2"><SIZE Height="1190" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="9550" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>y(t  _{0} )=y  _{0} ,````y(t  _{1} )=y  _{1}</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>y(t) : 상태변수(state variable)</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>u(t) : 통제변수(control variable), 부분연속함수 </CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>f, g는 세 변수(y, u, t)에 대해 미분가능한 연속함수</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="15" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="3"><CHAR>※ 변분학 문제는 최적제어문제의 특별한 경우로서 통제변수가 상태변수의 도함수이다.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="15" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="15" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>위의 문제는 정태적 최적화 문제와 같이 라그랑지함수를 도입하여 푼다.</CHAR><FOOTNOTE><PARALIST LineWrap="Break" LinkListID="0" LinkListIDNext="0" TextDirection="0" VertAlign="Top"><P ParaShape="1" Style="11"><TEXT CharShape="11"><AUTONUM Number="127" NumberType="Footnote"><AUTONUMFORMAT SuffixChar=")" Superscript="false" Type="Digit"/></AUTONUM><CHAR> 제약조건이 시간 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="72" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="2036563934" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="4"><SIZE Height="1177" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="4905" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>t  _{0}  LEQ t LEQ t  _{1}</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>의 범위에 있으므로 라그랑지승수가 아닌 t의 함수인 라그랑지함수를 도입한다. 다른 말로 ‘costate variable’ 이라 한다.</CHAR></TEXT></P></PARALIST></FOOTNOTE><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="15" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="15" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><EQUATION BaseLine="59" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="2036563933" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="3"><SIZE Height="2719" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="14700" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>max`````L=  int _{t  _{0}} ^{t  _{1}} {[f+ lambda (t)(g-y prime )]dt}</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>...............①</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="15" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="15" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>이 문제는 y, u, λ의 함수이므로 세 변수에 대해 미세 변동을 고려하여 문제를 푼다.</CHAR><FOOTNOTE><PARALIST LineWrap="Break" LinkListID="0" LinkListIDNext="0" TextDirection="0" VertAlign="Top"><P ParaShape="1" Style="11"><TEXT CharShape="11"><AUTONUM Number="128" NumberType="Footnote"><AUTONUMFORMAT SuffixChar=")" Superscript="false" Type="Digit"/></AUTONUM><CHAR> 정태적인 경우 세 변수에 관해 미분함으로써 필요조건을 도출할 수 있지만 최적제어문제의 경우 변수가 t의 함수이므로 바로 미분할 수 없고 변수의 변동을 고려한다.</CHAR></TEXT></P></PARALIST></FOOTNOTE><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="15" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="15" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="0"><CHAR>1 단계)</CHAR></TEXT><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR> 변분학에서와 같이 λ(t)의 변동을 고려</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="15" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR> </CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="15" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>①을 만족하는 최적경로를 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="86" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="2036563953" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="13"><SIZE Height="975" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="2390" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>lambda *(t)</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>라 하면</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="15" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="15" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><EQUATION BaseLine="86" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="2036563942" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="5"><SIZE Height="975" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="8920" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>lambda (t)= lambda *(t)+ epsilon h(t)</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="15" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="15" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>이를 ①에 대입하면</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="15" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="15" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><EQUATION BaseLine="59" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="2036563943" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="6"><SIZE Height="2719" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="15485" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>L( epsilon )=  int _{t  _{0}} ^{t  _{1}} {[f+( lambda *+ epsilon h)(g-y prime )]dt}</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="15" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="15" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>ε=0 일 때 극대화조건을 만족해야 하므로</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="15" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="15" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><EQUATION BaseLine="59" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="2036563944" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="7"><SIZE Height="2719" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="11135" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>{dL} over {d epsilon } =  int _{t  _{0}} ^{t  _{1}} {h(g-y prime )dt=0}</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="15" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="15" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>h에 관계없이 만족하려면</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="15" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR> </CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="15" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><TABLE BorderFill="3" CellSpacing="0" ColCount="1" PageBreak="Cell" RepeatHeader="true" RowCount="1"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="2036868968" Lock="false" NumberingType="Table" TextWrap="TopAndBottom" ZOrder="25"><SIZE Height="2414" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="9411" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Column" TreatAsChar="false" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="283" Left="283" Right="283" Top="283"/></SHAPEOBJECT><INSIDEMARGIN Bottom="141" Left="510" Right="510" Top="141"/><ROW