 HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="6215" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>mu '`=`( rho -r) mu ``</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="15" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="15" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>②, ⑥을 대입하면</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="15" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="15" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><EQUATION BaseLine="86" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="2137502651" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="216"><SIZE Height="1000" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="7415" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>u '' c'`=`( rho -r)u prime ``</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR> </CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="15" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="15" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>양변을 c로 나누고 u</CHAR></TEXT><TEXT CharShape="5"><CHAR>“</CHAR></TEXT><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>을 이항하면</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="15" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="15" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><EQUATION BaseLine="66" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="2137502653" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="217"><SIZE Height="2250" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="9000" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>{c'} over {c} `=`-(r- rho ) {u'} over {cu''} ``</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="15" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="15" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>앞과 같은 결과이다. </CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="15" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="15" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>즉, 현재가치 해밀토니안과 당기가치 해밀토니안은 같은 결과를 낳는다.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="14" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>(풀이끝)</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="15" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="15" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="1"><CHAR>라그랑지승수(costate variable)의 의미</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="15" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="18" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>최대화원칙은 정태적 최대화 문제의 해결에서 사용했던 라그란지안 기법의 동태적 일반화이다. 따라서 해의 민감도에 관해 같은 의미를 갖는다. 단 라그랑지승수가 단일 수치가 아니라 t의 함수이므로 t의 값에 따라 변한다는 점이다. 따라서 라그랑지승수의 의미도 기간과 관련되서 해석되어야 한다.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="15" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="15" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>최적값 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="86" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="2039891516" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="103"><SIZE Height="1000" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="4430" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>lambda *,`y*,`u*</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>을 적용한 범함수의 최대값이 다음과 같다고 하면</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="15" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="15" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><EQUATION BaseLine="59" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="2039891512" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="100"><SIZE Height="2719" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="29775" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>L*=  int _{t  _{0}} ^{t  _{1}} {(H(y*,`u*,`t,` lambda *)+ lambda * prime y`)dt} -[ lambda *(t  _{1} )y*(t  _{1} )- lambda *(t  _{0} )y*(t  _{0} )]</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="15" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="15" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><EQUATION BaseLine="61" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="2039891513" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="101"><SIZE Height="2452" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="7280" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>{Partial L*} over {Partial y(t  _{1} )} =- lambda (t  _{1} )</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR> , </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="61" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="2039891515" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="102"><SIZE Height="2452" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="6525" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>{Partial L*} over {Partial y(t  _{0} )} = lambda (t  _{0} )</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="15" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="15" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>초기 라그랑지승수는 초기 상태변수의 변화에 따른 목적함수의 최적값의 변화를 의미</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="15" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>최종 라그랑지승수는 최종 상태변수의 변화에 따른 목적함수의 최적값의 변화를 의미</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="15" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="15" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>목적함수가 비용, 가격 등 경제적 가치와 관련되어 있다면 라그랑지승수는 기회비용(shadow price)의 의미를 가진다.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="15" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="15" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="15" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="1"><CHAR>최적제어문제(optimal control problem)와 변분학(calculus of variation)과의 관계</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="15" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="1"/></P><P ParaShape="15" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>변분학의 문제</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="15" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><EQUATION BaseLine="59" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="2038222016" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="79"><SIZE Height="2719" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="9415" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>it max````  int _{t  _{0}} ^{t  _{1}} {f(y,`y prime ,`t)dt}</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR><TAB/></CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><EQUATION BaseLine="72" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="2038222017" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="80"><SIZE Height="1190" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="6915" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>s.t```````````y(t  _{0} )=y  _{0}</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR> , </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="72" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="2038222018" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="81"><SIZE Height="1177" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="4340" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>y(t  _{1} )=y  _{1}</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="15" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>변분학에서 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="86" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="2038222027" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="85"><SIZE Height="975" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="825" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" Hor