umberingType="Equation" ZOrder="131"><SIZE Height="1190" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="3070" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>lambda   _{2} `&gt;`0</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>  이면 u = 1 일 때 최대값</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="15" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><EQUATION BaseLine="72" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="2042551494" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="132"><SIZE Height="1190" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="3070" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>lambda   _{2} `&lt;`0</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>  이면 u = -1 일 때 최대값</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="15" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="15" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>부호함수는 다음과 같이 정의된다.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="15" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="15" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>z &gt; 0 이면 sgn(z) =1</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="15" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>z &lt; 0 이면 sgn(z) =-1</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="15" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="15" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>따라서 최적통제변수값 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="86" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="2042152536" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="126"><SIZE Height="975" Heig