ue" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>it max``````  int _{0} ^{INF } {e  ^{-rt}} [pf(L,K)-wL- rho I]dt</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="15" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><EQUATION BaseLine="86" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1392240974" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="249"><SIZE Height="1000" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="7950" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>s.t`````````````K prime =I- delta K</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR> </CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="15" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="15" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>p(t) ; t 시점에서 생산물 가격</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="15" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>r(t)=r ; 이자율 또는 투자수익률(시간에 상관없이 일정)</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="15" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="15" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="15" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>(풀이)</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="15" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>상태변수는 K(t), 통제변수는 L(t), I(t)</CHAR><FOOTNOTE><PARALIST LineWrap="Break" LinkListID="0" LinkListIDNext="0" TextDirection="0" VertAlign="Top"><P ParaShape="1" Style="11"><TEXT CharShape="11"><AUTONUM Number="164" NumberType="Footnote"><AUTONUMFORMAT SuffixChar=")" Superscript="false" Type="Digit"/></AUTONUM><CHAR> 목적범함수에는 표기의 편의상 각 변수가 시간 t의 함수임을 생략했다.</CHAR></TEXT></P></PARALIST></FOOTNOTE><CHAR> </CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="15" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="15" Style="0"><TEXT CharS