ENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>f(k*)- theta k*=c`*</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="15" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="15" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>앞의 Solow-Swan 모형에서 황금률 경제성장경로는 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="76" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1392241073" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="395"><SIZE Height="1365" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="4565" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>f prime (k  _{S} ^{*} )= theta </SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR> 를 만족시키는 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="76" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1392241074" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="396"><SIZE Height="1365" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="2270" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>k  _{S} ^{*} (t)</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR> 이었다.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="15" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="15" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>본 Ramsey모형은 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="86" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1392241075" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="397"><SIZE Height="975" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="6165" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION Aff